metadata.title: RZ/V2H: Pre-trained AI Model Compatibility with the RZ/V Series

sections.content:
Question:
Can trained AI models used with other RZ/V Series be used on the RZ/V2H?
Answer:
AI models will require reconversion with DRP-AI TVM. Since the type of ONNX operator supported by the tool differs in some cases, please check the manuals for the DRP-AI Translator and DRP-AI TVM.
Suitable Products
RZ/V2H
